      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 2.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects V.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>孟懿子問孝。子曰：「無違。」樊遲御，子吿之曰：「孟孫問孝於我，我對曰：『無違。』」樊遲曰：「何謂也？」子曰：「生，事之以禮；死，葬之以禮，祭之以禮。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Mang I asked what filial piety was. The Master said, "It is not being disobedient." Soon after, as Fan Ch'ih was driving him, the Master told him, saying, "Mang-sun asked me what filial piety was, and I answered him,—'not being disobedient.'" Fan Ch'ih said, "What did you mean?" The Master replied, "That parents, when alive, be served according to propriety; that, when dead, they should be buried according to propriety; and that they should be sacrificed to according to propriety."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-02-weizheng__006__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
