      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 2.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects VI.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>孟武伯問孝。子曰：「父母，唯其疾之憂。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Mang Wu asked what filial piety was. The Master said, "Parents are anxious lest their children should be sick."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-02-weizheng__007__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
      <prop type="x-work-id">lunyu</prop>
