      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 2.7</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects VII.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子游問孝。子曰：「今之孝者，是謂能養。至於犬馬，皆能有養。不敬，何以別乎？」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Tsze-yu asked what filial piety was. The Master said, "The filial piety of now-a-days means the support of one's parents. But dogs and horses likewise are able to do something in the way of support;—without reverence, what is there to distinguish the one support given from the other?"</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-02-weizheng__008__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
      <prop type="x-work-id">lunyu</prop>
