      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 2.8</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects VIII.8</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子夏問孝。子曰：「色難。有事，弟子服其勞；有酒食，先生饌。曾是以爲孝乎？」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Tsze-hsia asked what filial piety was. The Master said, "The difficulty is with the countenance. If, when their elders have any troublesome affairs, the young take the toil of them, and if, when the young have wine and food, they set them before their elders, is this to be considered filial piety?"</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-02-weizheng__009__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
      <prop type="x-work-id">lunyu</prop>
