      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 2.9</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects IX.9</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「吾與回言終日，不違如愚。退而省其私，亦足以發。回也不愚。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "I have talked with Hui for a whole day, and he has not made any objection to anything I said;—as if he were stupid. He has retired, and I have examined his conduct when away from me, and found him able to illustrate my teachings. Hui!—He is not stupid."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-02-weizheng__010__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
