      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「溫故而知新，可以爲師矣。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "If a man keeps cherishing his old knowledge, so as continually to be acquiring new, he may be a teacher of others."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
