      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「由，誨女知之乎！知之爲知之，不知爲不知，是知也。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "Yu, shall I teach you what knowledge is? When you know a thing, to hold that you know it; and when you do not know a thing, to allow that you do not know it;—this is knowledge."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-02-weizheng__018__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
