      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 2.20</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects XX.20</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>季康子問：「使民敬忠以勸，如之何？」子曰：「臨之以莊，則敬；孝慈，則忠；擧善而教不能，則勸。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Chi K'ang asked how to cause the people to reverence their ruler, to be faithful to him, and to go on to nerve themselves to virtue. The Master said, "Let him preside over them with gravity;—then they will reverence him. Let him be filial and kind to all;—then they will be faithful to him. Let him advance the good and teach the incompetent;—then they will eagerly seek to be virtuous."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-02-weizheng__021__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
      <prop type="x-work-id">lunyu</prop>
