      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「非其鬼而祭之，諂也。見義不爲，無勇也。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "For a man to sacrifice to a spirit which does not belong to him is flattery. "To see what is right and not to do it is want of courage."</seg>
